# The on-prem installer download (~800MB of 7-Zip chunks: FlowAccel-Setup-*.7z.*
# and FlowAccel-Package-*.7z.*) must NOT ship to Vercel - it blows the deployment
# size limit (this is what left the cloud site empty). The installer is for the
# IIS-hosted on-prem server; download it from GitHub release-chunks/ instead.
frontend/public/installer/

